# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# MichiKanji — environment variable reference
# Copy this file to .env.local for local development.
# In production (Vercel), add variables via Settings → Environment Variables.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# RESEND — email delivery
# Required for inquiry form email notifications (Option A).
# Get your API key at https://resend.com → API Keys.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
RESEND_API_KEY=re_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# INQUIRY_WEBHOOK_URL — generic webhook notification (Option B, optional)
# Set this to receive a ping in Slack, Discord, Zapier, Make.com, or n8n
# whenever someone submits the /advertise inquiry form.
#
# ⚠️  This is NOT the Resend webhook (/api/webhook/resend).
#     It is a separate HTTP POST endpoint provided by your chat/automation tool.
#
# Examples (replace the angle-bracket placeholders with your actual URL):
#   Slack:    Get URL from your Slack workspace → Apps → Incoming Webhooks
#   Discord:  Server Settings → Integrations → Webhooks → New Webhook → Copy URL
#   Zapier:   Create a "Webhooks by Zapier" Catch Hook trigger and copy the URL
#
# At least one of RESEND_API_KEY or INQUIRY_WEBHOOK_URL must be set so that
# inquiry form submissions reach you.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# INQUIRY_WEBHOOK_URL=<paste your webhook URL here>
